[Name] Haskell-Xmobar
[Summary] A Minimalistic Text-Based Status Bar
[Description] Xmobar is a minimalistic text-based status bar.  Inspired by the Ion3 status bar, it supports similar features like dynamic color management, output templates, and extensibility through plugins.
[License] BSD3
[Homepage] http://code.haskell.org/~arossato/xmobar
